          "reviewBody": "school is provided Where good & quality education. They have very trained & enthusiastic & co-operative staff for preprimary to higher level classes.\nSchool environment is also friendly , holistic too.\nEach every activity, projects, cultural programs have taken in the school as per our Indian culture & for mental,social growth of every child.\n\nParent of primary student.",
