            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Best school in the vicinity for quality education, discipline and culture.\nMost dedicated , highly trained and motivated staff. Each child has been given full attention to excel to his/ her best potential. Use of latest technology in education is USP of this school.\nIn sports it's the only school with biggest ground and best facilities .\nRun by a charitable trust so whole saving is reinvested for betterment of students , staff and upgradation of infrastructure.\nManagement team is professionally qualified and working selflessly for brighter future of students.\nOverall best value for money.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
