            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I love my school. We have lots of awesome books in the library. Our classrooms are spacious. The teachers are very friendly, though they see that we are all disciplined and well-behaved. I enjoy our e-Learning sessions as they are a fun way of learning. Besides the library, my favourite place is the Open air classroom and state-of-the-art Computer Lab. After school it is fun to pick up the Tamarind, and Jamun fruits or simply watch how the squirrels play on the trees in the school campus ! I love to play Chess and practice for sports under the guidance of our Sports Teachers.",
